<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
	<title>BRAVO</title>
	<style>
		* {
			font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;
			background-color: black;
			color: white;
		}

		h1 {
			text-align: center;
		}

		#winners {
			text-align: center;
			margin-top: 5vh;
		}

		span {
			margin-right: 50px;
		}

		img.mdr {
			width: 20vw;
		}

		img#ahah {
			margin-left: 10vw
		}

		img#winner {
			width: 100px;
			border-radius: 100%
		}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<h1>BIEN JOUÉ !</h1>
	<img id="ahah" class="mdr"
		src="https://media0.giphy.com/media/yoJC2GnSClbPOkV0eA/giphy.gif?cid=790b76115d2cb1464153335132451adb&rid=giphy.gif"
		alt="ahah">
	<img id="monney" class="mdr"
		src="https://media1.giphy.com/media/JpG2A9P3dPHXaTYrwu/giphy.gif?cid=790b76115d2cade8375076716345e4ac&rid=giphy.gif"
		alt="monney">
	<img id="mdr" class="mdr"
		src="https://media0.giphy.com/media/TgFibAJdezKXUYsddv/giphy.gif?cid=790b76115d2cacea446f723067d51f4b&rid=giphy.gif"
		alt="mdr">
	<img id="haha" src="https://pijnackersebridgeclub.nl/Toernooi/images/8345_In_bewerking.gif" alt="haha">
	<div id="winners">
		Tu es prêt à conquerir le monde. Enfin... là c'est juste le classement des coa mais bon...
		<br>
		Tu as gagné <%= nb %> points de coa.
		<br>
	</div>
<script src="https://unpkg.com/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
<script>
	var winners = document.getElementById("winners")

	axios.get('/api/winners')
		.then(response => {
			users = response.data;
			for (i in users) {
				winners.innerHTML +=
					"<span><img id='winner' src='https://media0.giphy.com/media/IB9foBA4PVkKA/source.gif'><a target='_blank' href='https://profile.intra.42.fr/users/" +
					users[i].login + "'>" + users[i].login + "</a> " + users[i].total_points +
					" pts</span>"
			}
		})
		.catch(error => {
			console.log(error);
		})
</script>
</body>

</html>
